title: Rob Bell - Jesus Wants To Save Christians - iTunes AudioBook
description:
Rob Bell & Don Golden

Jesus Wants To Save Christians - A Manifesto For The Church In Exile



iTunes AudioBook

Bookmarkable, cover art.

If you have an iPod, this is the file you want.	



Guys, PLEASE seed. I don't have a great connection, and it's not 24/7, so once you have downloaded it, please seed it for a week or longer. It's not a big file!


Can't download?? Upgrade your Torrent client to a version that can handle encrypted transfers. I ONLY do encrypted transfers.



And apologies to Rob Bell. The people downloading these would never buy them anyway, so you have lost nothing, and your prophetic voice simply needs to get out to the masses any way it can.
